MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 1/34/1/2003-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 30th December, 2003
9 Pausa, 1925(S).
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 30th December,
2003 :-
Shri M. Kannappan relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
State (Independent charge) of the Ministry of Non-Conventional Energy
Sources;
i)
The Prime Minister assumed the charge of the office of Minister of Non-
Conventional Energy Sources; and
ii)
Shri Gingee N. Ramachandran relinquished the charge of the office of
Minister of State in the Ministry of Textiles.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 5802
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to Deputy Chairman and
Members of the
Planning Commission.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)

(P. Gopalakrishnan)

(P. Gopalakrishnan)
